00:19:34.690 --> 00:19:39.400
to Japan in the '70s and
'80s, but it came right back

00:19:39.400 --> 00:19:43.390
with the IT innovation wave in
the '90s, which Japan missed.

00:19:43.390 --> 00:19:47.860
So when you put your economy
